## 输出要求
请输出严格符合以下 schema 的 JSON：
{
  "device": {
    "station": "变电站名",
    "voltage_kv": <int>,
    "equipment_type": "线路保护|母线保护|变压器保护|主变中性点保护|其他",
    "equipment_name": "线路/母线/主变名",
    "protection_set": "第一套|第二套|单套"
  },
  "protection_device": {
    "vendor": "厂家名",
    "model_raw": "原型号字符串",
    "model_base": "基础型号（如 PCS-931）",
    "firmware_version": "软件版本",
    "device_id": "装置 ID"
  },
  "equipment_params": {
    "ct_ratio_primary": <int>,
    "ct_ratio_secondary": <int>,
    "pt_ratio_primary": <int>,
    "pt_ratio_secondary": <int>,
    "rated_current_a": <float>
  },
  "settings": [
    {
      "item_no": "序号",
      "name_raw": "定值项原名",
      "value": "原值字符串",
      "value_numeric": <float or null>,
      "unit": "单位 or null",
      "function": "所属保护功能"
    }
  ],
  "control_words": [
    {
      "name_raw": "控制字原名",
      "value": "0/1 或 hex 字符串",
      "meaning": "投退/含义"
    }
  ],
  "trip_matrix": null,  // 如有则填 {format: "hex", entries: [...]}
  "parse_warnings": ["抽取中遇到的问题"]
}

注意事项：
1. 抽不到则填 null 并在 parse_warnings 记录
2. value_numeric 仅在明显是数字时填
3. firmware_version 提取 "V4.10" 等形式
4. 严格按 JSON 输出，不要有解释性文字